title: PestWorld Attendees Invited to MGK Booth to Play Kahoot!
text: Subscribe PestWorld Attendees Invited to MGK Booth to Play Kahoot! MGK is inviting PestWorld attendees to stop by their PestWorld booth (#469) and play a fun, interactive game called Kahoot! October 9, 2015 MGK is inviting PestWorld attendees to stop by their PestWorld booth (#469) and play a fun, interactive game called Kahoot! Attendees can test their knowledge of MGK products for a chance to win a Vivosmart fitness band, gift cards or a Yeti tumbler. Games are scheduled for Tuesday Oct. 20 at 4 p.m., Wednesday, Oct. 21 at 11 a.m., and Thursday, Oct. 22 at 11 a.m.
